
Apparently this simple thing has a wide variety of uses. I hope I will write a complete 
version, but for now...

Some of the uses includes:
- Useful
- - cleaning carpets
- - cleaning burnt vessels
- - removing smell from things (sometimes used in combination with vinnegar. Further search is required)

- Medical
- - lowering acid from stomach
- - treating mouth ulcer (canker sores at least?)
- - whitening teeth
- - lowering mouth bacteria reproduction
